)==false otherwise returns a snapshot\\n     *         of the DB after this operation.\\n     */\\n    public Snapshot put(byte[] key, byte[] value, WriteOptions options) throws DBException;\\n\\n    /**\\n     * @return null if options.isSnapshot()==false otherwise returns a snapshot\\n     *         of the DB after this operation.\\n     */\\n    public Snapshot delete(byte[] key, WriteOptions options) throws DBException;\\n\\n    /**\\n     * @return null if options.isSnapshot()==false otherwise returns a snapshot\\n     *         of the DB after this operation.\\n     */\\n    public Snapshot write(WriteBatch updates, WriteOptions options) throws DBException;\\n\\n    public Snapshot getSnapshot();\\n\\n    public long[] getApproximateSizes(Range ... ranges);\\n    public String getProperty(String name);\\n\\n    /**\\n     * Suspends any background compaction threads.  This methods\\n     * returns once the background compactions are suspended.\\n     */\\n    public void suspendCompactions() throws InterruptedException;\\n\\n    /**\\n     * Resumes the background compaction threads.\\n     */\\n    public void resumeCompactions();\\n\\n    /**\\n     * Force a compaction of the specified key range.\\n     *\\n     * @param begin if null then compaction start from the first key\\n     * @param end if null then compaction ends at the last key\\n     * @throws DBException\\n     */\\n    public void compactRange(byte[] begin, byte[] end) throws DBException;\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1782658862916}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.fusesource.leveldbjni:leveldbjni-all:1.8/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-28T15-01-39-305896Z.log:1809:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_7CUsgrqbTXIrrYUMX5ghK3Ni|fc_0a9d74a996958a30016a41372e7b24819095e95eec9dddb6ea\", \"toolName\": \"read\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"/**\\n * Copyright (C) 2011 the original author or auth